==The Series==

[[Image:Guineapig2 movie still2.jpg|thumb|right|[[I Am In Your Base Killing Your D00ds|I'M IN YOUR STOMACH RIPPING OUT UR ENTRAILZ]]]]
*'''The Devil's Experiment''': Some guy's kidnap a girl and torture her, to [[Shit nobody cares about|test the limits of pain]].
*'''Flower of Flesh and Blood''': A guy drugs a woman and cuts her into pieces while she is unconscious.
*[[An hero|'''He Never Dies''']]: A guy cuts apart his body and faps with his mutilated appendages for hours.
*'''Mermaid in a Manhole''': One of the gayer, more emo stories. An [[Joel Peter Witkin|artist]] finds a [[what|mermaid]] whose body is covered in blood and pus, and uses said blood and pus to paint her portrait.
*'''Android of Notre Dame''': A doctor tries to test out drugs on unwilling bodies provided to him by some guy, who gets pissed and hacks them up.
*[[transvestite|'''Devil Woman Doctor''']]: A tranny doctor who kills her patients. Fucking gay as shit.
*'''Slaughter Special''': Taking a look back at [[Unwarranted Self-Importance|all the great stuff]] we just saw!

==Charlie Sheen causes [[drama]]==
[[Image:Guineapig stfu.png|thumb|These films have also traumatised guinea pigs]]
While [[buttsecks|chilling]] with fellow [[hollywood]] [[faggots]] on a party with [[hookers and blow]], actor Charlie Sheen [[masturbation|watched]] "Flowers of Flesh and Blood" and being the complete [[retard]] that he is, mistook it for a real [[snuff]] flic and [[shit|shat]] himself in the process. He then went [[whining]] on his [[livejournal]] about how the [[movie]] [[pussy|scarred him for life]], that he can't [[eye bleach|unsee]] it and that [[bullshit|disgusting torture and murder videos like this should be banned to protect the nations youth from their negative influence]]. He also [[fellatio|complained]] to the [[FBI]] who then proceeded to send the [[party van]] to track down the [[sick fuck|makers of the movie]], only to find out that the [[shitty]] [[gore]] effects were indeed not real.

